[[Karinda Outpost]] was a [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] base set up on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Karinda]] in order to intercept [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Outer Rim]] communications. It was commanded by [[Colonel/Legends|Colonel]] [[Jarvis Tala]] and [[Lieutenant/Legends|Lieutenant]] [[Wes Gevar]]. They also had the [[Astromech droid/Legends|astromech droid]] [[R2-F7]] on the base, who was the [[Pilot/Legends|pilot]] of their [[Skiff/Legends|skiff]] while the base was under construction. A group of Rebels delivered supplies here from [[Greyman's Planet]] and were attacked by Imperial [[Scout trooper/Legends|biker scouts]] while they were going through the canyons en route to Karinda Outpost. They managed to get past the Imperials and delivered their cargo.

